        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This sprig of berry-festooned holly and mistletoe doesn't wilt or rot. It can be used as a primal locus, and it grants a +1 item bonus to Nature checks while you wear it.",
        "level": 6,
